  <brief_title>Effects of Victoza® Versus Lyxumia® on Gastroesophageal Reflux, Gastric Emptying and Gastric Acid Secretion</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of Victoza® (Liraglutide) Versus Lyxumia® (Lixisenatide) on Gastroesophageal Reflux, Gastric Emptying and Gastric Acid Secretion</official_title>
  <sponsors>
